            Summary = "How administrators use the State Withholding configuration dialog (Admin > Compliance) to see which states are ready for e-sign, which need a PDF uploaded, which accept the federal W-4, and which have no income tax — and how an employee's work location decides which form they get.",
            ContentType = TrainingContentType.Article,
